/**

module.exports = {

    /**
     * Define the style of UIBlockMagnet by default.
     */
    UIBlockMagnetInputFillColor: "#FFC107",
    UIBlockMagnetOutputFillColor: "#FF9800",
    UIBlockMagnetInputStrokeColor: "#6282CA",
    UIBlockMagnetOutputStrokeColor: "#FF6029",
    UIBlockMagnetDefaultWidth: 10,
    UIBlockMagnetDefaultHeight: 10,
    UIBlockMagnetDefaultRadius: 2,
    UIBlockMagnetDefaultName: "no_name",

    /**
     * Define the UIBlock style by default.
     */
    UIBlockFillColor: "#F44336",
    UIBlockStrokeColor: "#2E2C61",
    UIBlockDefaultWidth: 100,
    UIBlockDefaultHeight: 100,
    UIBlockDefaultRadius: 8,
    UIBlockDefaultHeaderHeight: 30,
    UIBlockDefaultUIBlockLinkOffset: 10,
    UIBlockDefaultTextOffset: 10,
    UIBlockDefaultFont: "18px Arial",
    UIBlockDefaultCorpusOffset: 30,
    UIBlockTextColor: "black",
    UIBlockShadowBlur: 2,
    UIBlockShadowColor: "rgba(0,0,0,0.5)",
    UIBlockHeaderColor: "#D32F2F",
    UIBlockDefaultTextColor: "#000000",

    /**
     * Define the UIBlockLink style by default.
     */
    UIBlockLinkCircleFillColor: "rgba(255, 95, 76, " + 0.5 + ")",
    UIBlockLinkCircleStrokeColor: "#8C0E00",
    UIBlockLinkLineStrokeColor: "#8C0E00",
    UIBlockLinkBezierCurveStrokeColor: "#333",
    UIBlockLinkDefaultCurveOffset: 50,
    UIBlockLinkDefaultCircleRadius: 10,
    UIBlockLineDefaultColor: "#424242",

    /**
     * Define the UIBlockFlow style by default.
     */
    UIBlockFlowFillColor: "#EBDE19",
    UIBlockFlowStrokeColor: "#9E9E9E",

    /**
     * Define the BlueprintBlock style by default.
     */
    BlueprintBlockColor: "#9C27B0",
    BlueprintBlockHeaderColor: "#7B1FA2",
    BlueprintBlockMagnetColor: "#4A148C",
    BlueprintBlockFlowColor: "#BA68C8"
};

name: VisualScripting/UI/UIVisualScripting.js
UIVisualScripting
description: Describe the UI class for Visual Scripting.

name: constructor
description: Construct the UI interface of the Visual Scripting canvas, and set the component's states.

params.name: props
params.description: Contains the properties of the JSX element.

name: _background
description: Contains the background of the canvas.

name: _handlers
description: Contains all the handlers which have been registered.

name: _guiObjects
description: Contains all the drawable objects.

name: state
description: Contains all the states of the React Component.

name: initHandlers
description: Initialize all the handlers that support the UI.

name: getCanvas
description: Returns the actual canvas of the UI.

name: componentDidMount
description: Initialize all the UI dependencies and register the UI to the canvas events.

name: componentDidUpdate
description: Draw all the objects that are in the canvas.

name: addDrawableObject
description: Allow to add new object in the canvas. The object has to inherit from UIDrawable class.

params.name: object
params.description: Contains the new object which will be draw on the canvas.

name: mouseDownHandler
description: Handle the mouse button down event.

params.name: e
params.description: Contains the event send by the canvas.

name: mouseUpHandler
description: Handle the mouse button up event.

params.name: e
params.description: Contains the event send by the canvas

name: mouseMoveHandler
description: Handle the mouse movement.

params.name: e
params.description: Contains the event send by the canvas.

name: addEventListener
description: Allow to register a callback to an event supported by the UI.

unknown.tagValue: {number} Returns the index of the callback in the registering list.

params.name: name
params.description: Contains the name of the event that the callback will be registered.

params.name: callback
params.description: Contains the callback function which will be called when the event is fired.

return.description: Returns the index of the callback in the registering list.

name: removeEventListener
description: Allow to remove a callback from an event.

unknown.tagValue: {boolean} Returns true if the removing has been done.

params.name: name
params.description: Contains the name of the event that the callback has been registered.

params.name: id
params.description: Contains the index in the registering list of the callback.

return.description: Returns true if the removing has been done.

name: showContextMenu
description: Show the context menu when the event is fired.

params.name: e
params.description: Contains the event fired by the canvas.

name: onContextMenuClose
description: Close the current context menu.

name: render
description: Render the Visual Scripting UI in the DOM.
